| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3776 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: a90d98b0-a9e5-5625-9241-43cbb797e14a"
index=* sourcetype=endpoint*
| where (CommandLine="*recoveryenabled no*" OR CommandLine="*bootstatuspolicy ignoreallfailures*") AND (process="*\bcdedit.exe")
